  "private": true,
  "description": "Next.js 16 (App Router) shell for scrum-poker. Server Components by default, Tailwind wired to @scrum-poker/config's shared preset, Sentry (Next SDK) for client + server, standalone output for Docker. Thin scaffolding only — real routes/UI/services land in later issues.",
  "license": "MIT",
